{"type":"step-attempt","step":"design","sessionId":"77f339a4-3aa9-4e2b-982b-6271823cbe19","outcome":{"verdict":"success","findingsPath":null,"error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"reason":"Wrote design.md, spec.md, and tasks.md under specrunner/changes/repo-root-resolve-exactly-once/ on branch change/repo-root-resolve-exactly-once-6eeee74e.\n\nPlan summary:\n- Convert the 9 listed handlers to consume the dispatch-injected CommandContext (repoRoot/invokerCwd) instead of re-resolving. Repo-required (init, inbox run, job prune, job cancel, job attach) → requiresRepo:true + unified dispatch error; repo-optional (job show, config effective, job resume→bootstrap) → degrade to ctx.repoRoot ?? invokerCwd with no re-resolution.\n- ps.ts is kept as a DI-fallback per the request; the job ls handler always passes ctx.repoRoot ?? invokerCwd so its internal resolveRepoRoot never fires in production.\n- Exactly-once tooth (T2): grep invariant over src/cli confining resolveRepoRoot* to a fixed CODEOWNERS-gated allowed set {command-context, doctor, load-config-with-overlay, ps}, plus a show-toplevel==0 assertion, liveness, and a break-confirmation regression guard.\n- CWD allowlist burn-down (T3): delete exactly CWD-init-git-spawn, CWD-job-show-root-resolve, CWD-inbox-debt, CWD-config-effective-di-default; no additions.\n- Identifier uniqueness (T4): replace the 4 B-13 references in the CWD ADR with the established CWD/T-05 identifier; model.md's StepExecutor B-13 untouched.\n\nDocumented consequences: init loses the git-unavailable diagnostic distinction (folded into the unified error, TC-002/TC-003 relocated to dispatch level); several direct-call tests need injection-seam updates (the churn the request permits). Scope stays within the change folder — no source edits performed; downstream implementer executes tasks.md.","status":"success"},"followUpAttempts":0,"transientRetryAttempts":0,"addedTurns":{"reportRetry":0,"postWork":0,"outputRepair":0}},"startedAt":"2026-07-20T08:49:29.816Z","endedAt":"2026-07-20T09:05:52.941Z","commitOid":"6ae9730e24103db4921a4c9f0b44ac46001f5e06"}
